Package com.crudetech.collections

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ForwardIterator<T>
    A simple GoF compatible iterator interface.
    LightweightStack<T>
    A lightweight stack interface to hide away the infamous Stack which itself derives from Vector.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractIterable<T>
    Simple base class for Iterables that provides an Arrays like implementation of Object.toString(), Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object).
    CircularIterable<T>
    A collection api compatible circular Iterable that lets you iterate endlessly over a given Iterable implementation.
    CollectionView<TView,TModel>
    A collection implementation that offers a projective view on another collection.
    EqualityComparable<T>
    A simple decorator that uses the supplied EqualityComparer implementation to compare the wrapped object.
    EqualityComparableMap<TKey,TValue>
    A Map adapter implementation that uses a passed in EqualityComparer instead of the build in Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object) methods.
    ForwardIterator.Builder  
    Iterables
    This class is very similar to Arrays except that it works for Iterables.
    ListStack<T>
    A simple stack implementation based on a List.
    ListView<TView,TModel>  
    Pair<F,S>
    A simple pair class that references two other objects.
    ReadOnlyCollection<T>
    A readonly collection wrapper.
    ReadOnlyList<T>
    A readonly list wrapper.
    SetView<TView,TModel>
